        "subject": "LU-3617 build: fix ofed configure check for newer RDMA events",
        "message": "LU-3617 build: fix ofed configure check for newer RDMA events\n\nThe configure check fails because include/rdma/ib_addr.h requires\nvlan_dev_vlan_id, which seems to be defined in\ninclude/scsi/fc_compat.h. Adding that header to the configure script\nfixes the test, and prevents LBUGs on those events.\n\nSigned-off-by: Kit Westneat <kwestneat@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I366b9fb3eed2d78bd5b27dc0c62e340e12c1e6af\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b1_8"
    }
